data.description: Discover this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath single-story corner lot home in the lovely Bulverde Village. With an open floor plan, the spacious living room flows effortlessly into the kitchen, making it perfect for family life and entertaining. The master bedroom is a cozy retreat featuring a tray ceiling, a walk-in closet, and a master bath with a garden tub. Another feature of this property is its unique location with no neighbor behind, as it backs onto a hilly greenbelt, offering additional privacy and a beautiful natural backdrop. The backyard is an ideal setting for outdoor entertaining, providing a peaceful space to enjoy gatherings or quiet evenings amidst nature.  Situated in a vibrant community, the home is conveniently located minutes  Located in a vibrant community, this home is just minutes away from Johnson High School, Cibolo Green Elementary School, as well as convenient shopping and the J.W. Marriott. Bulverde Village is known for its friendly atmosphere and great location, making this home an ideal choice for anyone looking for comfort and convenience in NEISD. Don't miss the chance to make this delightful house your new home.
